. * DESCRIBE AND CODEBOOK ARE USUALLY ENOUGH TO LEARN ABOUT YOUR DATA

. * REMEMBER DESCRIBE DESCRIBES ALL COMPLETE DATA

. * CODEBOOK DESCRIBE EACH VARIABLE IN DATA

. * YOU CAN DESCRIBE OR CODEBOOK INDIVIDUAL VARIABLES INSTEAD OF ALL DATA. YOU JUST 
> HAVE TO ATTACK THE VARIABLE TO THE COMMAND

